
-- Addon Storage Location
Interface/AddOns/stil_tihs/
├─ stil_tihs.toc
├─ stil_tihs.lua
├─ icon.tga          (minimap button)
└─ icon_arrow.tga    (radar arrow)

-- Addon Features
- Add / Remove current target buttons
- Scrollable/ Clickable/ Sorted watched player list
- Toggleable Features: Alert Once, Arrow Intensity, Show Arrow, Show Timer, Flash Alerts, Stealth Alerts
- Reset UI & Minimap button
-	Minimap arrow with smooth rotation
-	Arrow color gradient + intensity
-	Seconds-ago timer with matching color gradient
-	Saved minimap button position
